'''亞美尼亞死刑制度'''是在[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]刑法和宪法范围内执行的一种惩罚方法，直到2003年宪法修改后才予以废除。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=NTC - Bancadati|url=http://www.handsoffcain.info/bancadati/europe/armenia-50000102|website=www.handsoffcain.info|access-date=2020-05-27|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225121339/http://www.handsoffcain.info/bancadati/europe/armenia-50000102}}</ref>死刑的起源在亚美尼亚是不为人知的，但它仍然存在于1961年的亚美尼亚刑法中，该刑法一直执行和适用到1999年。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Republic of Armenia Criminal Code 1999|url=https://www.refworld.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rwmain/opendocpdf.pdf?reldoc=y&docid=52738f4a4}}</ref>亚美尼亚立法中纳入了死刑，并对死刑罪行实行死刑，这些罪行被列为可判处死刑的罪行，包括[[叛国|叛国]]、间谍活动、一级谋杀、[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]行为和严重军事罪行。<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|last=Maia & Tsira|first=K. & C.|date=2012|title=The abolition of the death penalty and its alternative sanction in South Caucasus: Armenia, Azerbaijan and Georgia|url=https://cdn.penalreform.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/South-Caucasus-Research-Report-Death-Penalty-and-Alternatives-ENGLISH.pdf|journal=|access-date=2021-03-02|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308104255/https://cdn.penalreform.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/South-Caucasus-Research-Report-Death-Penalty-and-Alternatives-ENGLISH.pdf}}</ref>

亚美尼亚最后一次公开使用死刑是在1991年，当时对着犯人头部开了一枪。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Refworld {{!}} Armenia: Time to abolish the death penalty|url=https://www.refworld.org/docid/3ae6a98a24.html|last=Refugees|first=United Nations High Commissioner for|website=Refworld|language=en|access-date=2020-05-27}}</ref>在此之后，死刑被暂停执行，并受到了来自国内<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=Armenia: Debate Over Death Penalty Threatens Council Of Europe Membership|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/1096917.html|website=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty|language=en|access-date=2020-05-27|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126224726/https://www.rferl.org/a/1096917.html}}</ref>和国际组织的严厉批评。<ref name=":3" />
